@startuml 采集滞后-下沉备份
participant 业务App
participant VFS
participant UlogFS
participant SpillThread
Database TmpFS
Database DiskCache
participant logtail

业务App -> VFS : write 写入日志
VFS -> UlogFS : write 写入日志
UlogFS -> TmpFS : write 写入日志
note over TmpFS: consumed = 0 (未读)

note over SpillThread: 水位超限
activate SpillThread
SpillThread -> TmpFS : 读取数据
SpillThread -> DiskCache : 写入副本
note over TmpFS: 未读块 → 不打洞！保留数据
deactivate SpillThread

logtail -> TmpFS : read 读取(正常读到数据)
logtail -> UlogFS : 上报已读区间
@enduml